<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE theorem	SYSTEM "../Symbols.dtd">
<theorem xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
	xmlns="http://webmath.math.ualberta.ca/v1/Theorem"
	xsi:schemaLocation="http://webmath.math.ualberta.ca/v1/Theorem    http://webmath.math.ualberta.ca/Schemas/v1/Theorem.xsd"
	type="Proposition"
	id="Thm_RREFMatrix">
	<caption>Shape of an RREF cofficient matrix</caption>
	<statement>
		<para>An augmented coefficient matrix in RREF has the following form</para>
		<math.display>
			<latex>
				<![CDATA[
\begin{array}{ccccccccccccccc|c}
0 & \cdots & 0 & 1 & * & \cdots & * & 0 & * & \cdots & * & 0 & * & \cdots & * & {\color{blue} d_1 } \\
0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 1 & * & \cdots & * & 0 & * & \cdots & * & {\color{blue} d_2 } \\
\vdots &   &   & \vdots & &     &   & \vdots & &     &   & \vdots & &     & \vdots & {\color{blue} \vdots } \\
\vdots &   &   & \vdots & &     &   & \vdots & &     &   & \vdots & &     & \vdots & {\color{blue} \vdots } \\
0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 1 & * & \cdots & * & {\color{blue} d_r } \\
0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & {\color{blue} * } \\
\vdots &   &   & \vdots & &     &   & \vdots & &     &   & \vdots & &     & \vdots & {\color{blue} \vdots } \\
0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & {\color{blue} 0 }
\end{array}
				]]>
			</latex>
		</math.display>
		<para>The <latex>{*}</latex> in the augmentation column of the <latex>(r+1)</latex>-st row is either a <latex>0</latex> or a <latex>1</latex>. If it is a <latex>1</latex>, then <latex>d_1=\cdots =d_r=0</latex>.</para>
	</statement>
</theorem>